	Define spinning progress reporter unconditionally
	* rudel-compat.el (header): updated copyright
	(progress-spinner-values):
	(progress-reporter-update):
	(make-progress-reporter):
	(progress-reporter-force-update):
	(progress-reporter-spinner-p):
	(progress-reporter-spin): move out of conditional definition since
	Emacs does not contain the patch in any version

